      <title>中国年轻人通过玩彩票缓解经济焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/young-chinese-ease-their-angst-over-economy-by-playing-lottery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的彩票店正在抛弃平淡无奇的店面，将自己重塑为时尚人士聚会的场所，其口号吸引着受到经济放缓打击的年轻人，以快速致富的诱惑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/young-chinese-ease-their-angst-over-economy-by-playing-lottery</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
